WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
What Actually Moves Outcomes

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Most teams discuss practical, but the real bottleneck is decision quality in live execution.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Define the baseline first, then test one intervention before scaling it wider.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Convert one recurring meeting into a decision review with explicit next actions.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
This approach compounds because each cycle keeps what works and drops what does not.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Start small, document what changed, and promote only patterns that hold under pressure.
